    detailEn:
      "Celestial robe episodes in later Taketori offshoots and drama show moon envoys reclaiming Kaguya’s robe and dissolving mortal memory, echoing the core parting theme. Read sequels as layered performance texts, not undifferentiated from the Heian core; heavenly dress law ends earthly attachment. This précis stays documentary rather than novelistic and invites comparison with regional variants. This précis stays documentary rather than novelistic and invites comparison with regional variants. This précis stays documentary rather than novelistic and invites comparison with regional variants.",
